title: Treading Water (2001)
description:
Treading Water (2001)


Starring: Angela Redman, Nina Landey, Annette Miller, Robert Harte, Richard Snee
Directed by: Lauren Himmel
Produced by: Lauren Himmel, Julia Hollinger


Casey is a longshorewoman who seems to have everything: she lives on a boat with her beautiful social worker girlfriend Alex, and they are very much in love. But there's nothing like the holidays to bring out the drama of the average family. Casey has rejected her privileged upbringing and restores old boats for a living. What she can't reject is her deep attachment to her family living just across the bay. When the Olsens come together for Christmas, the unwrapping of the presents takes a back seat to the unraveling of emotions..
